      {
        "content": "Arbitrary external call with user-controlled target and calldata\n\nexecute(address target, bytes data) performs target.call(data) without an allowlist, letting an attacker make the contract call any address \u2014 including token approvals draining the contract's own holdings. Fix: restrict targets/selectors via an allowlist; never forward arbitrary calldata from untrusted callers.",
